saṃyutta nikāya 35
1. aniccavagga
2. ajjhattadukkhasutta
“cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ.
yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;
yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ.
sotaṃ dukkhaṃ … pe …
ghānaṃ dukkhaṃ …
jivhā dukkhā …
kāyo dukkho …
mano dukkho.
yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā;
yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ.
evaṃ passaṃ … pe …
nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti.
dutiyaṃ.
